lead_paragraph: An article on Sunday about the high expectations for the University of Florida football team misstated the name of the poll in which the Gators are ranked No. 1 this preseason. It is the USA Today Top 25 Coaches’ Poll, not the ESPN/USA Today coaches poll. (ESPN and USA Today do, however, collaborate on a college basketball poll.).
